title: The Gourmet Offensive Falafel Bar
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Organic, Mediterranean, Fast food, Salad bar, Take-out, Middle Eastern
description: Little upstairs cafe offering falafel, baba ganoush, curry, gado gado, halloumi, soup and chips. There is a toppings bar with sauces (beetroot ketchup, hot chilli and chilli lime and corriander) and pickled veggies.
